snippet.title: Rayman Lum'o'Grams - World Premiere Trailer | Rayman Alive 2023
snippet.description:
✨ HER RETRIBUTION WAS INEVITABLE ✨

Introducing our new Rayman fan game in the genre of Picross - "Rayman LumoGrams - Rayman Picross Fan Game", revealing new gameplay details, as well as the first details of the story, featuring The Muse of Poets, the second goddess of The Glade of Dreams, as an antagonist, mentioned in the Rayman 2 guide, but never got into any of the games about Rayman! 🔥

Learn more: https://linktr.ee/RaymanUniverse

Rayfanpedia page: https://fan.raymanpc.com/wiki/Rayman_Lum%27o%27Grams
Game Jolt page: https://gamejolt.com/games/Rayman-Lum-O-Grams/770177
Rayman Pirate-Community thread: https://raymanpc.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=74974
YouTube playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuPsL6XLzlYyTU8LyQjoGk9uwPAnV_9zD

🌟First Public Demo - Early 2024!🌟

Follow us:
Discord: https://discord.gg/s3k53PujJD
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RUniverseVK
VK: https://vk.com/raymanuniverse
